message: Hello! Welcome to Better Deal Insurance. My name is Chris. How can I assist you today?
Hi Chris! I'm feeling really happy today as I just got a new car and need to update my insurance details.
That's great to hear! Before we proceed, can you confirm your full name for security purposes?
Of course! My full name is Sarah Smith.
Great, thank you for completing security. Can you now confirm your date of birth?
Sure, my date of birth is 10/09/1985.
Perfect, thank you for that. To proceed further, can you confirm the first line of your address and postcode?
My address is 123 Green Street, London, NW1 5SE.
Thank you, Sarah. Lastly, could you confirm your email address for me?
Thank you for completing security. I appreciate your cooperation. How can I assist you with your insurance update today?
I was hoping to update my car insurance policy to include my new vehicle. Can you help me with that?
Absolutely, Sarah. Let's see how we can assist you. Let me run through your account details first.
Thank you, Chris. I appreciate your help with this.
I've reviewed your account, Sarah. It seems we need some additional information to process the update. Would you mind providing the registration number of your new car?
I don't have that information on hand right now. Can we update it later?
I completely understand, Sarah. Let's go with that option. Please provide the registration number at your earliest convenience so we can update your policy accordingly.
Sounds good, Chris. Thank you for your assistance today. I will get back to you with the registration number soon.
You're welcome, Sarah. I'm glad that I was able to help. Feel free to reach out whenever you have the details. Have a great day!
